Title: Terry Fator Live In Concert Digital

reviewText: I have Terry Fator's first DVD and have nearly worn it out.  I expect this one to have the same fate.  Terry is the best ventriloquist around and sounds more like the artists that he mimics that the artists themselves.  I followed him when he won "America's Got Talent" and predicted he would make it big.  My daughter and her husband caught his show in Las Vegas and it was the highlight of their trip.
Title: Terry Fator Live In Concert Digital

Title: Terry Fator Live In Concert Digital

reviewText: Terry Fator is very good at what he does! I watched his new dvd and loved it. I am speechless with his voice talents. I'd say he is the best Ventriloquist/Entertainer ever! Sorry Jeff Dunham.....His show was so much fun to watch. Not a dull moment! Great songs, and funny likeable puppets. I like the fact that Terry gives back to others too. He's a great all around person! Keep up the good work Terry! Hope to see many more shows! Highly recommend this dvd! You will enjoy every minute, great extras too.
Title: Terry Fator Live In Concert Digital
